{"tid":2335471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第一個估NBA 賽果既平台正式上線啦!","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:29:47.000Z","uid":387162,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b47b1da20d560444bb0a3d50d4974706cda022","tid":2335471,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘿~同大家講個好消息呀~~<br />\n籃估隨住常規賽既步伐，一齊響12月21日正式運作啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，籃估即係估NBA 籃球比賽既意思。有日忽發奇想，不如整個估賽果既龍虎榜，既可以增加投入感之餘，又可以作為茶餘飯後既話題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n籃估特點:<br />\n1. 玩法簡單，有倍數積分活動，有特殊任務，有排行榜<br />\n2. 唔使錢，成功註冊完就可以即時玩<br />\n3. 唔涉及任何賭博成份<br />\n<br />\n季尾總決賽後作結算。基於小弟資源有限，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暫時考慮頭 5名會有獎品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獎品詳情會容後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家支持下一齊玩，覺得好玩既可以分享比身邊鐘意睇波既朋友，同埋歡迎入去禁杯咖啡支持下小弟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門 : <a href=\"https://llclk.com/nba4funhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fllclk.com%2Fnba4funhk%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a5409064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://llclk.com/nba4funhk/</a>"},{"pid":"f3e4cb93acad457aa9b75e671aebe532f2581c57","tid":2335471,"uid":189626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"聽日開波！"},{"pid":"ee8359e48d9f80b4ba36694927cb034c3471eb3f","tid":2335471,"uid":366603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"NBA不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff31cfda822ee0ca7be4935759d8fd1a95e1886","tid":2335471,"uid":189626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee8359e48d9f80b4